snippet.title: Thus Spoke the Donke | Official Gameplay Trailer | 1
snippet.description:
Thus Spoke the Donke is brand new 2D, topdown, pixel-art immersive sim game by Wise Monke Entertainment Studio. To taste fascinating stealth - action game experience play the demo on June 10 for PC. 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2835760/Thus_Spoke_the_Donke/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/RRXcggnZGb
